.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-7-3::.
City: paris, london, san-francisco, edinburgh, hannover, boston, hamburg
The people prefer 7 different music-genres: ambient, blues, country, d&b, hip-hop, jazz, metal
 1. the fan of metal is between the person traveling to san-francisco and the fan of country##2
 2. the person traveling to london is somewhere to the right of the fan of blues##5
 3. the fan of blues is not the person traveling to edinburgh##6
 4. the fan of ambient is somewhere to the right of the fan of jazz##5
 5. the fan of ambient is between the fan of jazz and the person traveling to hannover##2
 6. the fan of country is somewhere to the right of the person traveling to edinburgh##5
 7. the person traveling to hamburg is on the far right##1
 8. the person traveling to edinburgh is on the left or right of the fan of d&b##3
 9. the person traveling to san-francisco is somewhere between the fan of hip-hop and the fan of metal##7
10. the fan of blues is on the left or right of the person traveling to london##3
11. the person traveling to hannover is in an even position##4
12. the person traveling to hannover is not the fan of ambient##6
13. the person traveling to boston is somewhere between the person traveling to london and the person traveling to hannover##7
14. the fan of d&b is on the left or right of the person traveling to hannover##3
15. the person traveling to san-francisco is on the left or right of the person traveling to hannover##3
16. the person traveling to hannover is not the fan of jazz##6
17. the person traveling to edinburgh is on the left or right of the fan of country##3
18. the person traveling to london is on the right of the person traveling to paris##1
19. the fan of ambient is somewhere to the left of the fan of hip-hop##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |     2      |     3     |    4    |       5       |     6     |      7      |
| City         | paris | london | boston | hannover  | san-francisco | edinburgh | hamburg |
| Music-Genre   | blues   | jazz       | ambient   | hip-hop | d&b           | metal     | country     |

