 8. the fan of reggae is on the far left##1
 9. the person driving the snowmobile is somewhere to the left of the fan of hip-hop##5
10. the fan of house is in an even position##4
11. the fan of house is somewhere between the fan of indie and the fan of blues##7
12. the person driving the skateboard is somewhere to the right of the fan of soul##5
13. the person driving the skateboard is on the left of the person driving the jet-ski##1
14. the fan of salsa is somewhere to the left of the person driving the van##5
15. the fan of soul is on the left or right of the person driving the skateboard##3
16. the person driving the snowmobile is somewhere to the left of the person driving the scooter##5
17. the person driving the skateboard is between the fan of house and the person driving the trike##2
