.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-7-5::.
7 different brands of cigars are smoked: siglo, cain, pall-mall, prince, swisher, blend, chaman
7 different pets are kept: cat, ferret, hamster, horse, lizard, rabbit, turtle
 1. the pall-mall-smoker is on the right of the swisher-smoker##1
 2. the owner of the rabbit is somewhere between the owner of the cat and the owner of the hamster##7
 3. the blend-smoker is on the far left##1
 4. the owner of the horse is not the blend-smoker##6
 5. the owner of the horse is somewhere to the left of the owner of the cat##5
 6. the cain-smoker is somewhere to the left of the swisher-smoker##5
 7. the swisher-smoker is somewhere to the left of the pall-mall-smoker##5
 8. the owner of the cat is somewhere to the left of the owner of the turtle##5
 9. the owner of the rabbit is not the swisher-smoker##6
10. the cain-smoker is somewhere to the left of the owner of the horse##5
11. the swisher-smoker is somewhere to the left of the prince-smoker##5
12. the pall-mall-smoker is the owner of the lizard##1
13. the cain-smoker is on the right of the blend-smoker##1
14. the cain-smoker is the owner of the ferret##1
15. the pall-mall-smoker is on the left of the chaman-smoker##1
16. the prince-smoker is on the left of the siglo-smoker##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |      2      |     3     |    4    |   5    |    6    |   7    |
| Cigar   | blend | cain | swisher | pall-mall | chaman | prince | siglo |
| Pet           | hamster     | ferret      | horse     | lizard  | rabbit | cat     | turtle |

