 1. the person who likes green is in the middle##1
 2. the person who's sport is biathlon is somewhere to the right of the person who's sport is weightlifting##5
 3. the person who likes green is on the right of the person who likes purple##1
 4. the person who likes lilac is somewhere between the person who likes red and the person who likes green##7
 5. the person who likes aquamarine is on the left of the person who likes lilac##1
 6. the person who likes lavender is the person who's sport is weightlifting##1
 7. the person who's sport is surfing is somewhere to the left of the person who likes aquamarine##5
 8. the person who's sport is basketball is not the person who likes lavender##6
 9. the person who likes aquamarine is somewhere to the right of the person who's sport is weightlifting##5
10. the person who's sport is snowboarding is not the person who likes lavender##6
11. the person who's sport is snowboarding is on the left or right of the person who's sport is biathlon##3
12. the person who likes aquamarine is on the left or right of the person who's sport is soccer##3
13. the person who likes green is not the person who's sport is biathlon##6
14. the person who likes aquamarine is the person who's sport is snowboarding##1
15. the person who's sport is biathlon is somewhere to the right of the person who likes aquamarine##5
16. the person who's sport is surfing is on the left of the person who's sport is soccer##1
17. the person who's sport is skateboarding is on the left or right of the person who likes purple##3

.:: Answer ::.
