 3. the person who growsdaffodil is the manager##1
 4. the mechanic is on the left of the person who growsmarigold##1
 5. the person who growsaconite is on the left of the person who growssunflower##1
 6. the person who growsmarigold is somewhere between the mechanic and the writer##7
 7. the person who growsdaffodil is on the left of the person who growsrose##1
