 6. the person who growsamaryllis is somewhere between the person who growsbegonia and the person who growssunflower##7
 7. the person eating lemon is in an odd position##4
 8. the person who growssunflower is in an even position##4
 9. the person eating mango is the person who growszinnia##1
10. the person eating strawberry is between the person eating raspberry and the person who growsamaryllis##2
