The people grow 7 different varities of flowers: balloon-flower, azalea, rose, dahlia, iris, daisy, orchid
 1. the person who's sport is skiing is somewhere between the person who growsiris and the person who growsdahlia##7
 2. the person who's sport is cricket is on the left or right of the person who growsazalea##3
 3. the person who growsorchid is between the person who's sport is swimming and the person who's sport is snowboarding##2
 4. the person who's sport is cricket is somewhere to the right of the person who growsrose##5
 5. the person who's sport is cycling is on the left of the person who's sport is handball##1
 6. the person who growsballoon-flower is on the left or right of the person who growsdahlia##3
 7. the person who's sport is cycling is somewhere to the right of the person who's sport is snowboarding##5
 8. the person who growsdaisy is the person who's sport is skiing##1
 9. the person who's sport is skiing is somewhere to the right of the person who growsiris##5
10. the person who growsorchid is on the left of the person who's sport is snowboarding##1
11. the person who's sport is handball is somewhere to the right of the person who's sport is snowboarding##5
12. the person who's sport is handball is on the left or right of the person who's sport is cycling##3
13. the person who growsballoon-flower is somewhere between the person who's sport is skiing and the person who growsdahlia##7
14. the person who's sport is snowboarding is the person who growsazalea##1
15. the person who growsorchid is the person who's sport is cricket##1
16. the person who growsorchid is on the left or right of the person who growsrose##3
17. the person who's sport is snowboarding is somewhere to the left of the person who's sport is tennis##5
18. the person who growsballoon-flower is on the right of the person who growsdaisy##1

